# Themify Icons

Installed via npm (`themify-icons` package). The compiled CSS uses `.icon-{name}` classes (NOT `ti-{name}`).

## Usage

- Use `<i class="icon-{name}"></i>` for all icons
- Font files are served from `/fonts/themify.*` (copied to each app's `public/fonts/`)

